title: The Complete Miss Silver Mystery Collection
description:
Audio Books : Mystery and Suspense : Other quality : English

All are unabridged CD quality (or near CD quality).
Of the 32 titles here, 10 are recorded at 32kbps / 22kHz Mono CBR and the rest are 48 kbps / 44 kHz Mono CBR.
All are narrated by Diana Bishop.
